        "body": "<p>Since everything is in a single class, it should separate code into methods for organization.<\/p>\n\n<p>You will need the main method, \"public static void main(...)\", however if you want to make any extra methods that are not contained within an another (instance) class then those methods need to be declared as static as well.<\/p>\n\n<p>So it would look something like this...<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public class RPS{\n\n    public static void main(String[] args){\n       play();\n    }\n\n    private static void play(){...}\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
